From: Valerie.Obenchain at roswellpark.org (Obenchain, Valerie)
Date: Mon, 30 Jan 2017 16:18:23 +0000
Subject: [Bioc-devel] tokay2: devel Windows builder
Message-ID: <DM5PR12MB157809F1665E15B6683E3C73FF4B0@DM5PR12MB1578.namprd12.prod.outlook.com>

Hi,

Just a heads up that we're having intermittent problems with the Windows
devel builder, tokay2, located on site at RPCI. About a week ago, RPCI
had a problem with back-up power that has since been resolved. Because
we continue to see problems with tokay2 (but none of the other servers)
it's possible a power supply was damaged or something else has gone wrong.

We are working on sorting this out. In the meantime, when tokay2 is not
responsive it will be pulled from the build report so only malbec2,
oaxaca and toluca2 will post. This will be the case for today's builds
(Jan 30).

Valerie



