Hi Leonardo,

You need the latest version of rtracklayer: 1.35.3. Unfortunately this
version didn't propagate because of an issue that is not related to
this:

 
https://bioconductor.org/checkResults/3.5/bioc-LATEST/rtracklayer/malbec2-checksrc.html

In the mean time you can fetch and install rtracklayer 1.35.3 directly
from svn.

Cheers,
H.

